com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.dom

Interface DOMNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DOMEventTarget, SearchContext
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DOMElement, DOMFormControlElement, DOMFormElement, DOMFrameElement, DOMInputElement, DOMOptionElement, DOMSelectElement, DOMTextAreaElement 

    public interface DOMNode
extends DOMEventTarget, SearchContext
    Represents a singe HTML DOM node in the document tree. All JxBrowser DOM objects implement the DOMNode interface.
    表示文档树中的单一HTML DOM节点。所有JxBrowser DOM对象都实现DOMNode接口。

      • getTextContent

        java.lang.String getTextContent()
        Returns text content of the node and its descendants.

        This method returns null if the element is a document, a document type, or a notation. To grab all of the text and CDATA data for the whole document.

        If the node is a CDATA section, a comment, a processing instruction, or a text node, this method returns the text inside this node (the getNodeValue()).

        For other node types, this method returns the concatenation of the textContent attribute value of every child node, excluding comments and processing instruction nodes. This is an empty string if the node has no children.

        Differences from innerText
        • Note that while textContent gets the content of all elements, including <script> and <style> elements, the mostly equivalent innerText property, does not.
        • innerText is also aware of style and will not return the text of hidden elements, whereas textContent will.
        • As innerText is aware of CSS styling, it will trigger a reflow, whereas textContent will not.
        返回节点及其后代的文本内容。如果元素是文档，文档类型或符号，则此方法返回null。抓取整个文档的所有文本和CDATA数据。如果该节点是CDATA节，注释，处理指令或文本节点，则此方法返回此节点内的文本（getNodeValue（））。对于其他节点类型，此方法返回每个子节点的textContent属性值的串联，不包括注释和处理指令节点。如果节点没有子节点，则为空字符串。与innerText的区别请注意，虽然textContent获取所有元素的内容，包括
        Returns:
        the text content of the node and its descendants. 节点及其后代的文本内容。
